"use client" import { useState, useEffect } from "react" import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom" import AppLayout from "../components/AppLayout" function Dashboard() { const [user, setUser] = useState(null) const [stats, setStats] = useState({ passwordsGenerated: 0, hashesCreated: 0, filesAnalyzed: 0, domainsChecked: 0, }) const [isLoading, setIsLoading] = useState(true) const navigate = useNavigate() useEffect(() => { // Vérifier si l'utilisateur est authentifié const auth = localStorage.getItem("auth") if (!auth) { navigate("/login") return } try { const userData = JSON.parse(auth) if (!userData.isAuthenticated) { navigate("/login") return } setUser(userData) // Simuler le chargement des statistiques setTimeout(() => { setStats({ passwordsGenerated: Math.floor(Math.random() * 50) + 10, hashesCreated: Math.floor(Math.random() * 30) + 5, filesAnalyzed: Math.floor(Math.random() * 20) + 3, domainsChecked: Math.floor(Math.random() * 15) + 2, }) setIsLoading(false) }, 1000) } catch (err) { navigate("/login") } }, [navigate]) const handleLogout = () => { localStorage.removeItem("auth") navigate("/login") } if (isLoading) { return (
) } return (
